- Smart Contract
    - Allow only one publisher to call updateState function
    - Record Orderer, Executor, and Publisher

- Publisher
    - Allow messages from one executor - address is recorded in Smart Contract

- Executor
    - Allow messages from one orderer - address is recorded in Smart Contract

- Watchtower
    - Create Watchtower who listens on Transactions and replays those
    - In case of state root differences, send message to Smart Contract
    - Penalize Executor

- Protocol
    - Add compression
    - Transaction fees
    - Revert state